event_name: Queer Line Dance x Wild Buffalo August 2025
location: Wild Buffalo House Of Music, 208 West Holly Street Bellingham, WA 98225 United States
description: Join us on Tue August 5th 2025 at 6:00 PM at Wild Buffalo for a night of fun, dancing, and community. Let's celebrate our community and love for line dancing in a welcoming and inclusive environment. Whether you're an experienced dancer or have never line danced in your life, all are welcome and we make this super approachable! Hosted by Alysondra of @greatenergyevents! A percentage of proceeds will be donated to Whatcom Youth Pride to support the important work they do in our community! Drinks for purchase from Wild Buffalo. Must be 21+!
